    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Post数据到服务端生成文件]]></title>
    <link href="http://agiledon.github.com/blog/2012/02/10/post-data-to-server-side-to-generate-file/"/>
    <updated>2012-02-10T11:27:00+08:00</updated>
